00:00:00,050 --> 00:00:00,962
TL;DR.

2
00:00:00,962 --> 00:00:03,087
This week in 30 seconds:.

3
00:00:03,087 --> 00:00:13,612
Government stake: The Trump administration is considering a direct equity stake in OpenAI — Trump publicly framed it as "making the American people a partner".

4
